CatDescriptText: The certificate the two men are holding reads, "North Carolina Mutual Life Insurance Company Certificate of Merit This Certificate is Presented to John David Lewis on the Occasion of His Retirement in Recognition of the Completion of thirty-five years Meritorious Service with the Company...December 1950".
TitMainTitle: Two men holding certificate that reads, "North Carolina Mutual Life Insurance Company Certificate of Merit This Certificate is Presented to John David Lewis...", with men and women seated at banquet table
